<v NARRATOR>Pacing is the deliberate variation of tempo across a story's five beats. It is what gives a told tale its shape.

7
00:00:51.065 --> 00:01:05.156
<v SLOW>A story has five beats. Hook. Setup. Rising. Turn. Close. Each beat has its own distinct tempo.

8
00:01:05.156 --> 00:01:16.327
<v SLOW>The Hook is fast. The Setup is steady. The Rising builds. The Turn is sharp. The Close is slow.

9
00:01:16.327 --> 00:01:24.218
