11
00:01:34.589 --> 00:01:46.680
<v NARRATOR>She demonstrates by walking the 5-beat arc, her tempo-trail a bright spark for the hook, then a steady line, then a coiling ribbon.

12
00:01:46.680 --> 00:01:58.331
<v NARRATOR>At the turn, the trail snaps with a brilliant flash. For the close, it becomes a long, serene stream that fades.

13
